      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEASIDE POND NZ (4) is a newcomer to the Gary Hall yard from NZ where he was last seen winning at Addington three months ago. He looks well placed to kick off in WA with a win. FABULOUS DREAM NZ (5) is flying this campaign with three wins from as many starts, all of them at this circuit and distance. Led from a similar barrier last week and cruised home by 8.5m. Hard to knock and could deliver again. A LITTLE SILENCE NZ (12) draws on the second line so may need a touch of luck but has has been going very well with a string of top-two finishes at this venue. SWEET PINS NZ (9) draws wide but drops in grade after attempting a G3 last week and came from the back row to win at Pinjarra prior.",
